data.name: COZY SWEATFLEECE MEGA STRAIGHT™ SWEATPANT
data.c_fit: Fit: Mega — Oversized with room to move
data.c_tabDescription:
Or just those cute new socks. As the straight-leg evolution of our beloved Mega Sweatpant, these pants feature the roomy silhouette you know and love, classic inseam pockets and an infinity loop drawcord. They’re made with Cozy Fleece — premium midweight fleece famous for its soft-brushed back, sueded face and cloud-nine plush feel. The best kind of cozy.

Faded Colours: Our unique wash is achieved through a special technique — instead of dyeing the fabric, we dye the finished garment for a dimensional, sun-faded look and lived-in soft feel.
data.c_tabDetails:
• Content: 78% cotton, 22% polyester, exclusive of ornamentation
  • Care: Machine wash
  • Imported
